{"tid":41824,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"欠千萬巨債兼婚變 地產AA觀塘站跳橋亡","createTime":"2016-12-16T07:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T02:02:29.000Z","uid":65346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24640e1d695319d7b6269c2abf718cdc5f50f4a3","tid":41824,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n昨晚11時許，市民行經港鐵觀塘站D2出口行人天橋，發現一名男子倒卧樓梯上，昏迷不醒，於是報警。警員及救護員接報到場，經檢驗證實該名男子經已身亡。同時在對上往月華街的升降機外，撿獲一件懷疑屬於死者的外套，相信他跨過圍欄，從7層樓高的電梯出口位跳下。<br />\n死者姓余39歲，半年前與妻子離婚後搬出兩人愛巢，及後他搬入將軍澳一間酒店居住，警方在其入住的酒店找到銀行追數的欠單，疑因做生意欠下千萬元巨債，懷疑他欠債及加上離婚雙重打擊而尋死，出事後，警方聯絡其胞兄了解事件。"},{"pid":"9e69d2ae23440daeb6c652d27245fc5ad5d08c2f","tid":41824,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:07:26.000Z","msg":"個世界咁唔公平,  死左都好既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037984a94a01bb06105a27546e88235719bb5cc5","tid":41824,"uid":8167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:15:23.000Z","msg":"死左 唔洗還錢嘛<br />\n千萬點撚還 屌佢老味"},{"pid":"27355b150d0e317481c6c7fb20643995fee872bd","tid":41824,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:19:38.000Z","msg":"點解跳樓要除外套，減低風阻？"},{"pid":"d83c1a51fc82ab8f0b9590efa905fa7857c7f26e","tid":41824,"uid":54486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:35:14.000Z","msg":"其實著草返大陸山區隱居得唔得？幾十萬都夠安老"},{"pid":"8cde3e439a54bd3223e85c456e6aa036f526cd97","tid":41824,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:38:30.000Z","msg":"AA?<br />\n<br />\n邊度寫"},{"pid":"16d5ae5494cfd411e8feece026ae9a7d346d043d","tid":41824,"uid":7171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個世界咁唔公平,  死左都好既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好做傻事"},{"pid":"11b2af0aded27eba8f10b5d995d588ba8f8b0903","tid":41824,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:48:17.000Z","msg":"好快到我"},{"pid":"cbb0c18ca1142e51f0ef7f4548e91e7d1d542f76","tid":41824,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死左 唔洗還錢嘛<br />\n千萬點撚還 屌佢老味</blockquote><br />\n爭銀行錢駛撚還咩，你慌唔係爭公仔佬錢咩"},{"pid":"c24e9f475241c3a93d2f7d54f98f0813e8cb360a","tid":41824,"uid":17680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"香港人真係慘"},{"pid":"e46d6e4611f24beb27478580fff0cd622a25e4f1","tid":41824,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:52:55.000Z","msg":"新生趣？"},{"pid":"b3cded012dfc95b0b71e02c56fa1f2d675fe9aff","tid":41824,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>死左 唔洗還錢嘛<br />\n千萬點撚還 屌佢老味</blockquote><br />\n爭銀行錢駛撚還咩，你慌唔係爭公仔佬錢咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算金牌 AA，始終唔係固定收入，銀行唔會借得多。"},{"pid":"a8e2561898697592a0c2401831555b1f7cb1d19f","tid":41824,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:48:24.000Z","msg":"千萬元巨債<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b364cc2dbb50c7d5e14997d6a2bc830aec216721","tid":41824,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:18:09.000Z","msg":"究竟邊處寫死者係AA?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734b993503714899df81fb458bc38a1bfebd6b74","tid":41824,"uid":10201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"前美聯高層"},{"pid":"1357b9d53d9d5a524e1a4a8f0a701d72e28799de","tid":41824,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161216/56053514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161216%2F56053514&d=O%2F2QtF72%2ByUTb5qDpHHNkwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=ea7049c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161216%2F56053514&h=1b0ba9f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161216/56053514</a><br />\n<br />\n【17:55 更新】死者為美聯高級物業顧問。<br />\n【11:50】死者為商人，欠下千七萬巨債。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚11時許，市民行經港鐵觀塘站D2出口行人天橋，發現一名男子倒卧樓梯上，昏迷不醒，於是報警。警員及救護員接報到場，經檢驗證實該名男子經已身亡。同時在對上往月華街的升降機外，撿獲一件懷疑屬於死者的外套，相信他跨過圍欄，從7層樓高的電梯出口位跳下。<br />\n死者余卓偉，39歲，三年前結婚，與妻育有一名9個月大女兒，惟好景不常，兩夫婦感情生變，半年前與妻子離婚後搬出兩人愛巢，及後他搬入將軍澳一間酒店居住，警方在其入住的酒店找到銀行追數的欠單，疑因做生意欠下1,700萬元巨債，懷疑他欠債及加上離婚雙重打擊而尋死，出事後，警方聯絡其胞兄了解事件。"},{"pid":"3168f509b8e7826cc91d14b99d95341ee9a6a853","tid":41824,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:14:30.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》曾致電余的胞兄，但他表示不願多談。根據資料，余生前曾在美聯任職元朗錦綉花園助理區域經理，並與另外3名美聯高層組成「炒樓四人幫」，於2010年大手購入上水天巒的洋房，他其後離職，至今年6月疑因要放售單位套現，遂將該洋房沽出，勁蝕320萬元。據悉，近日余因欠債窮途沒路，數日前「回巢」美聯，由高層變成「散仔」，任職商業部高級物業顧問。<br />\n美聯工商舖發言人表示，對余的不幸去世深表惋惜，並對其家人致以深切慰問。"},{"pid":"e35d75cd0db31e969b68c158f8e7abca46c19654","tid":41824,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:15:38.000Z","msg":"成日&quot;低調&quot;置業 post  果幾位., 在 hkg, lihkg R 唔到客...下年好快上路 !"},{"pid":"564c4aa2053440eb666e4fbd5e9a2220e6a2759e","tid":41824,"uid":43717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:19:27.000Z","msg":"差銀行錢就老破搞撚掂啦<br />\n一定唔只銀行條數"},{"pid":"864d9a0119d1651f3800d5d5da3546f921b4807f","tid":41824,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":